0.08     MyD*+ pi+ pi-                     PHOTOS PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay MyD_0*-

Decay MyD_0*0
0.08    MyD*+ pi- pi0                      PHOTOS PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay MyAntiD_0*0

Decay MyD'_10
